Package com.github.dm.jrt.android.retrofit

Retrofit adapters and utility classes specific to the Android platform.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ComparableCall<T>
    Decorator implementation making a call instance comparable (that is, equals(Object) and hashCode() methods are properly implemented.
    ContextAdapterFactory
    Abstract implementation of a call adapter factory, providing an automatic way to create Context invocation factories to be used to handle Retrofit calls.
    RequestData
    Class used to make an OkHttp request data parcelable.
    ServiceAdapterFactory
    Implementation of a call adapter factory supporting Channel and StreamBuilder return types.
    ServiceAdapterFactory.Builder
    Builder of Service routine adapter factory instances.
    ServiceCallInvocation
    Implementation of a Context invocation handling OkHttp requests.
